{"tid":669893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"她控男同事「單手戴套」性侵　法官難以置信","createTime":"2018-05-19T00:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T06:39:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1182af957399657d17dff19371a08f515db1dcc9","tid":669893,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T00:56:36.000Z","msg":"小玲控告遭男同事阿雄（皆為化名）性侵，稱對方壓制她，另隻手拿保險套、用嘴咬開戴保險套，法官認為，對方不太可能僅用單手戴保險套，台中地院以缺乏積極證據，判他無罪。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，去年1月2日晚間，阿雄邀小玲吃晚餐，之後向她央求，因流汗想到附近旅館洗澡用餐，請她陪同。兩人抵達汽車旅館，小玲在床上看電視，他之後也坐到床邊，突以手摸她胸部。<br />\n<br />\n小玲嚐試推開，他繼續將對方衣物褪去，以一手戴上保險套，性侵被害人。法官認為，難以想像他是如何在她不斷掙扎抵抗之情形下，僅以一隻手完成戴保險套的動作？合議庭以無積極證據證明性侵犯行，判無罪。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180519/640_4e271c22e985e075c8169e3e1345680e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180519%2F640_4e271c22e985e075c8169e3e1345680e.jpg&h=25d3ae6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180519/1356862/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180519%2F1356862%2F&d=rFtWNqMKfEyI6LBGuj2FC2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=13e4104b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180519%2F1356862%2F&h=4bf786ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180519/1356862/</a>"},{"pid":"f99bc166cca8d569496f85414fb2d84656e373a0","tid":669893,"uid":90593,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T01:08:07.000Z","msg":"又係台灣。。。"},{"pid":"00f92a728632ce7b52431f9e3a897a672c5a5675","tid":669893,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T01:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c3fa83abc168a2f99cd0a510008956869a2066","tid":669893,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy